Facilitate seamless integration between the DBS system and the D365 application to ensure accurate and timely synchronization of vendor-related data.
Automate Vendor PO creation updates in D365 whenever a new Vendor PO is created in the DBS system.
Ensure synchronization of vendor information updates so that any modifications to vendor records in the DBS system are reflected in D365 in real-time.
Establish a one-way data flow from the DBS system to D365, ensuring that all vendor creation and update processes originate exclusively from the DBS system.
Maintain data consistency and accuracy by implementing a robust integration mechanism that aligns with the mapped fields between DBS and D365.
Simplify and streamline the vendor management process by reducing manual interventions and leveraging automation for record synchronization.
